    32Рєњ## Intro<a name="intro"></a>
    34РєњTomli is a Python library for parsing [TOML](https://toml.io).
    35РєњVersion 2.4.0 and later are compatible with [TOML v1.1.0](https://toml.io/en/v1.1.0).
    36РєњOlder versions are [TOML v1.0.0](https://toml.io/en/v1.0.0) compatible.
    37Рєњ
      РєњРђд
