   152Рєњ## FAQ<a name="faq"></a>
   154Рєњ### Why this parser?<a name="why-this-parser"></a>
   156Рєњ- it's lil'
   157Рєњ- pure Python with zero dependencies
   158Рєњ- the fastest pure Python parser [\*](#pure-python):
   159Рєњ  14x as fast as [tomlkit](https://pypi.org/project/tomlkit/),
   160Рєњ  2.1x as fast as [toml](https://pypi.org/project/toml/)
      РєњРђд
   201Рєњ## Performance<a name="performance"></a>
   203РєњThe `benchmark/` folder in this repository contains a performance benchmark for comparing the various Python TOML parsers.
