     1Рєњ# `tomllib` РђЊ Tomli in the standard library
     3РєњTomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
     4Рєњ
     5РєњRelevant links:
     6Рєњ
     7Рєњ- Python Issue Tracker: https://bugs.python.org/issue40059
      РєњРђд
    13Рєњ## Converting Tomli to tomllib Рђд
    15Рєњ### Sync status
    17Рєњ`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18Рєњmatches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19Рєњ
    20Рєњ### Steps to convert
    22Рєњ- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
    23Рєњ
